== 东京博物馆

#table(
  columns: (auto, auto),
  img("assets/ttj-day4-05.avif"),
  img("assets/ttj-day4-08.avif"),
  img("assets/ttj-day4-06.avif"),
  img("assets/ttj-day4-07.avif"),
